{
  "stem": "26111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the man comes out and says that-- in very hypocritical language-- says, all Jewish ladies and gentlemen are requested to please vacate the theater, since the-- since certain, certain party bigwigs are about to, to take their places in the theater.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they can't be in the same room-- unthinkable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they will go to the box office and get their money back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so I went to the box office, got my money back, which was actually not true, because all they did-- you gave them-- was the address.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they'd send you the money, which they never did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So even there, they screwed you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was a blow to me because I had-- well, it's, it's a matter of refuges.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You look for refuges.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where can you go that you aren't being-- aren't being well, at best, demoralized, at worst, beaten up, somewhere in-between humiliated, insulted, et cetera?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where do you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the opera house-- dark, anonymous in the audience-- had been one of those places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now it was dangerous, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, after Kristallnacht, there was no more of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, very few.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very few.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few went-- by that time, very few Jews went to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, in fact, I had some arguments with, with fellow students, with, with friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, you shouldn't go to those bastards', you know, those, those bastards' theaters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, I'm not going to let them deprive me culturally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Until the-- until they won't let me, until they forbid me-- once they forbid it, I won't go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I won't pretend to be-- to be a-- to be a Christian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But why not?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They couldn't give me a good reason why not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
